<DOC><DOCNO> DOE1-75-0102 </DOCNO><TEXT>This article highlights some of the most significant developments andtrends evident currently in exploration drilling. Most are related tothe search for improved efficiency, greater economy and productivity.Many of the examples come from European practice with Scandinavia beinga strong centre for new developments; this largely reflects the highcost of labour and the broad spread of hard and difficult rocks to bedrilled there. 5 figs.</TEXT></DOC>